{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_53_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 工具セットどうするのよ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一月三日　朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1433.3332936,
          "startTime": 2.2333332936
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと早く目が覚めちゃったわね\nまぁ今日の収録は午前中だし、いっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "さてと、遙子お手製の野菜たっぷりスムージーを\n飲んでお仕事に備えるとしますか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14933.333333300003,
          "startTime": 29.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "うぅーん……今、こっちから声がしたような……\nあ、いたいた、遙子さ～ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5233.333333400001,
          "startTime": 31.6666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7256.666666699999,
          "startTime": 33.69
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん？　めずらしいわねこんなに朝早く\nあと、怜ちゃんが見てる遙子はただの壁よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "誕生日プレゼント……私、今日は遠出で帰りが\n遅くなるから……いる間に渡しておこうと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9666692097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "朝が苦手な怜ちゃんが私のために……感激だわっ！\nそれと、今話しかけてる遙子は植木鉢よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.4666692097,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5566.664377899997,
          "startTime": 67.0333335876
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12366.669466000005,
          "startTime": 73.8333386757
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "お誕生日、おめでとうございます……\nこれ、野菜の盛り合わせセットです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.8000053406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "二日酔いの日に……ぬか漬けを食べてるって聞いたので\n……合いそうなものを、選びました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "どれも、味が良さそうでしょう……\nほら、このナスなんて、特に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "本当ね！　カチカチで重みもズッシリ！\nまるで鉄みたいな……ってトンカチ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "これお野菜セットじゃないわ！　工具セットよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3666811229,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14999.988341199994,
          "startTime": 123.3666694641
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "んー……工具ぅ？　何言ってるんですかぁ？\nこの人参なんて、こんなに美味しそうなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.6000027974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "それは五寸釘！　絶対に食べちゃダメよ！\nこんなの漬けたってなんにもならないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.2000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、これが本当の糠に釘――\n……って言ってる場合かーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "うぅー……なんなんですか、さっきから大声出して……\nあ、遙子さん……朝からお酒飲んでたんですね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.000007375,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drink-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13299.992879299993,
          "startTime": 162.3000002543
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "ダメですよぉ、これから仕事なんですから……\nはい、これは没収です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.4000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ～！　遙子のお手製スムージー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.7666938386,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 20099.97308230001,
          "startTime": 184.8666669209
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ～……私はまだ時間あるので、もう少し\n寝てます……では、遙子さん……良い誕生日を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.1333335876,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9266.666666700019,
          "startTime": 186.4000002543
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、怜ちゃん！？　私のスムージー……\nというか、この工具セットどうするのよ～！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.7999931334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.3833493155
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.3833493155
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "お、おかしいわ……早起きして遙子さんに会いに行った\n気がするんだけど、その時の記憶が全くない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.8999890644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 207.0333305359
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "なんで五寸釘を握りしめてたの……？　それにあの緑の\n液体は何っ！？　一体何してたのよ、私……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.0333193461,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}